# Readex Pro font binaries (declared in pubspec.yaml, family ReadexPro).
#
# These four .ttf files are REAL Readex Pro (SIL Open Font License 1.1), each
# containing BOTH Latin and Arabic glyphs:
#   ReadexPro-Regular.ttf  (400)
#   ReadexPro-Medium.ttf   (500)
#   ReadexPro-SemiBold.ttf (600)
#   ReadexPro-Bold.ttf     (700)
#
# They were generated from the @fontsource Readex Pro release (woff2 → ttf,
# Latin + Arabic subsets merged per weight). Replace them with the official
# Google Fonts binaries any time — keep the same filenames; no other change
# needed. (They previously shipped as empty placeholders, which made CanvasKit
# render no text on the web build — real glyph-bearing files are required.)
